>宣布推出名人版<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-traitors"><i>《叛徒》</i></a> ，并确认该剧将回归常规节目第四季。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="453" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-features/the-traitors-soundtrack-cover-songs-3576402"><b>赞扬《叛徒》及其极其精彩的翻唱歌曲</b></a></li></ul><p>该真人秀节目由克劳迪娅·温克尔曼 (Claudia Winkleman) 主持，参赛者将在苏格兰高地的一座城堡里争夺高达 12 万英镑的奖金。</p><p>当他们到达城堡时，一小部分人被选为“叛徒”，他们必须消灭“忠实”参赛者才能获得奖品。然而，如果后者能够通过每日圆桌会议找出并驱逐欺骗性的参赛者，他们就会赢得现金奖励。</p><p>该剧迄今为止已播出两季，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/who-won-the-traitors-season-two-3577895">在之前委托播出的第三季（预计将于 2025 年初）之前</a>，BBC 曾表示，首个名人版本将在广播中播出。 </p><figure id="attachment_3572687" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3572687" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3572687" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Claudia-Winkleman-The-Traitors-2.jpg" alt="克劳迪娅·温克曼" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Claudia-Winkleman-The-Traitors-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Claudia-Winkleman-The-Traitors-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Claudia-Winkleman-The-Traitors-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Claudia-Winkleman-The-Traitors-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Claudia-Winkleman-The-Traitors-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Claudia-Winkleman-The-Traitors-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw,